            <div class="maindetail">
                <div class="title">本馆大事记 </div>
                <a href="#" target="_blank" id="a3d"><i class="threed"></i></a>
                <div class="tip"><span>时间：2015.01.06</span>
                <span>浏览次数：10210</span>
                    </div>
                <div class="cont">
                    <table class="MsoNormalTable" border="1" cellpadding="0" style="border: 1pt solid windowtext;"><tbody><tr class="firstRow"><td width="120" colspan="2" style="border: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:    16px;font-family:宋体;">2019</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">年3月29日</span></p></td><td width="700" style="border-top: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-left: none; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">外交部“外交外事知识进党校”培训组到我馆参观考察。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="120" colspan="2" style="border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:    16px;font-family:宋体;">2019</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">年3月21日</span></p></td><td width="700" style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">湖北省委常委、宣传部长王艳玲同志来我馆调研。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="120" colspan="2" style="border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:    16px;font-family:宋体;">2019</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">年3月12日</span></p></td><td width="700" style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">湖北省暨武汉市纪念孙中山逝世94周年纪念仪式在我馆举行。仪式结束后，省政协常务副主席李兵、省政府副秘书长刘仲初一行参观我馆。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="120" colspan="2" style="border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:    16px;font-family:宋体;">2019</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">年3月8日</span></p></td><td width="700" style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">举办主题为“着装魅力与形象礼仪”的专题讲座。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="120" colspan="2" style="border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:    16px;font-family:宋体;">2019</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">年3月6日</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">—8日</span></p></td><td width="700" style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">与十堰市博物馆联合在武昌水果湖第一小学、武昌实验小学、湖北省第二保育院开展了《从“禁锢”到“解放”——纪念三八妇女节》专题社教活动。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="120" colspan="2" style="border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:    16px;font-family:宋体;">2019</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">年3月4日</span></p></td><td width="700" style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">与十堰博物馆联合在武汉经济技术开发区（汉南区）黄陵小学4个班级开展“传承历史文化 弘扬雷锋精神”研学活动。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="120" colspan="2" valign="top" style="border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 4px 9px;"><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">2019</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">年1月29日</span></p></td><td width="700" style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">举办中小学生辛亥名人字画临摹活动。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="120" colspan="2" valign="top" style="border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 4px 9px;"><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">2019</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">年1月29日</span></p></td><td width="700" style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">《剑胆琴心——辛亥名人翰墨展》在东配楼二楼临展厅开幕。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="120" colspan="2" style="border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:    16px;font-family:宋体;">2019</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">年1月22日</span></p></td><td width="700" style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">应急管理部、文化和旅游部和国家文物局组成的博物馆和文物建筑消防安全大检查督导调研组到馆开展督导调研工作。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="120" colspan="2" style="border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:    16px;font-family:宋体;">2019</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;">年1月21日</span></p></td><td width="700" style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 4px 9px;"><p style="margin-top:9px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:9px;margin-left:0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:16px;fon